    && add-apt-repository -y ppa:borglab/gtsam-release-4.0 \
    && apt-get update \
    && apt install --no-install-recommends -y libgtsam-dev libgtsam-unstable-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

    && catkin_make
